  <h2>Science Fairs</h2>

<img src="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/images/science-fair-display-board.jpg" class="imgposLeft" alt="" >

 <p>Time for your school science fair project? Don't Panic! Just follow these simple step-by-step instructions to create your winning entry!

<br> </p>

<h3>Pick a Great Topic</h3>

<p>The first step is choosing the right science fair project idea, based on your interests and abilities.</p>

<ul>

<li>Get <a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/science_fair_project_idea.html">science fair topics and project ideas</a>.</li>

<li>Discover the different <a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/school_science_fair_project.html">types of science fair projects</a> and how to choose the right one.</li>

<li>How to <a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/science_fair_topic.html">pick the best idea</a> for you.</li>

<li>See <a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/samplescienceprojects.html">sample projects</a> (great for middle school and high school students).</li>

</ul>





<h3>Design and Complete your Project</h3>

<p>After you pick a topic, the next step is planning your experiment, followed by completing your project and then presenting your results.</p>

<ul>

<li>The <a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/scientific_method.html">scientific method</a> - What is it and why is it important?

<li><a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/science_fair_experiment.html">Design a valid science experiment</a>.</li>

<li>Tips for performing your project.</li>

<li><a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/lab_safety.html">Collecting data safely and accurately</a> - laboratory and experimental safety, lab notebooks and keeping accurate research records.</li>

<li><a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/scientific_method.html#CONCLUSION">Analyzing your data</a> and results, and reaching a conclusion.</li>

<li>The <a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/science_fair_display.html">science fair display board</a> - preparing your report and presentation. </li>

<li><a href=" http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/winning_science_fair_project.html">What do the judges want?</a></li>

<li><a href="http://www.sciencemadesimple.com/science_fairs_parents.html">For Parents</a> - 5 valuable benefits for your child

</ul>







